data.description: **$10,000 seller concession to be offered for Buyer to use toward closing costs or a rate buy down.** Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a rare 3-car garage and bonus space. Embrace sustainable living with the inclusion of solar panels that not only contribute to a greener environment but also offer significant energy savings. The spacious back porch is an ideal space for entertaining, whether you're hosting lively gatherings or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. Step into the heart of the home - a recently updated kitchen that seamlessly combines modern aesthetics with practical functionality. From sleek countertops to contemporary fixtures, this kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight. The harmony of style and convenience extends to the recently upgraded floors, providing a fresh and welcoming ambiance throughout. With thoughtfully designed spaces this home is a testament to a modern lifestyle. *Front yard has been digitally enhanced. Living room and breakfast area are virtually staged. BBQ pit and outside bar convey. Solar panels will be paid off at closing by seller. Existing sprinkler system is not in working condition.*
